
# Product Page Images

This directory contains images for product-related pages.

## Image Guidelines:
- Recommended size: 1200x800px for hero images, 300x300px for product thumbnails
- Format: JPG or PNG
- Quality: High resolution for crisp display

## How to Add Images:
1. Upload your image files to this directory
2. Update the image paths in src/data/productPageContent.ts
3. Update the alt text for accessibility

## Suggested Images:
- products-hero.jpg - Product catalog hero image
- category-banners/ - Folder for category-specific banners
- product-showcase.jpg - Featured products showcase
